- **CSV**: Built-in `Blob` + download.
- **Charts**: Recharts (already in your stack).
- **Local Save/Share**: URLSearchParams + localStorage.
- All client-side → zero cost, instant, works offline after load.

**Traffic Proof**: “free mortgage calculator with PDF download 2026” + “mortgage amortization excel free” = high-intent keywords almost no one ranks for yet.

